19:46.393 --> 19:47.978
Really? That's super cool.

19:48.061 --> 19:52.691
Our ethos is to serve everyone. And we've
made a safe place for a lot of people

19:52.774 --> 19:54.193
from the trans community

19:54.276 --> 19:59.239
who have otherwise had
emotionally, uh, disturbing experiences

19:59.323 --> 20:01.408
at the classic binary retail environment.

20:01.491 --> 20:02.910
We're here to help.

20:02.993 --> 20:05.204
He just bought this in for us today.

20:05.287 --> 20:08.498
-Okay, that's nice. Yeah.
-This is your suit.

20:08.582 --> 20:10.334
-That's nice.
-We wanted fabric

20:10.626 --> 20:13.462
that is classic.
The finishings are gorgeous.

20:13.545 --> 20:16.048
-[Skyler] Yeah, I like that a lot.
-[Tan] Yeah.

20:16.131 --> 20:18.592
Let's get you in this,
we want to see you in it.

20:20.761 --> 20:24.765
A lot of our trans male clientele come
and say I need a men's suit.

20:24.848 --> 20:27.935
So, what we do is
we bind the chest tighter.

20:28.018 --> 20:31.605
We give more room in the true waist
to reduce the skirting effect.

20:31.772 --> 20:35.692
We make the hips in the jacket about
two inches smaller than the hipbone.

20:35.776 --> 20:36.902
It straightens it out.

20:36.985 --> 20:40.614
I never would have realized those
tiny tweaks make such a difference.

20:40.864 --> 20:43.033
People think it's rocket science,
it's not.

20:43.116 --> 20:45.744
Let's put your hands behind your back.

20:52.501 --> 20:55.170
-[Tan] Um, I see you smiling.
-Yeah.

20:55.295 --> 20:56.964
-It makes me so happy.
-Yeah.

20:57.047 --> 20:59.216
This being, like, the first time

20:59.299 --> 21:02.135
I've really tried on clothes
since surgery.

21:03.095 --> 21:05.305
I did lipo around my belt line

21:05.389 --> 21:08.892
because I was self-conscious
about how wide my hips were.

21:08.976 --> 21:10.852
And I was not very broad up top.

21:10.936 --> 21:14.273
And now I look like this.
And that's what I want.

21:14.356 --> 21:17.192
And the suit is showing that
and that's exciting.

21:17.276 --> 21:18.568
Get your body back.

21:18.652 --> 21:22.155
It's the first time I've seen that
so that's why I can't stop smiling.

21:22.239 --> 21:23.824
-Good.
-Yeah.

21:24.408 --> 21:26.994
I love it. Thank you, good job. Yes.

21:27.077 --> 21:29.037
I want one, too. Thank you.

21:30.205 --> 21:32.374
I don't wanna take it off.

21:32.457 --> 21:34.793
