which I love.

21:34.876 --> 21:36.795
No, that's exactly what we want.

21:36.878 --> 21:38.130
-Hang it for me.
-Okay.

21:38.213 --> 21:40.465
Then Daniel
can make these alterations.

21:40.549 --> 21:41.967
[Skyler] Yeah, of course.

21:42.551 --> 21:44.094
-Thank you.
-My pleasure.

21:44.177 --> 21:46.013
It looks fantastic.

21:48.432 --> 21:51.601
When you looked in that mirror,
