21:51.685 --> 21:53.061
I felt like there I was.

21:53.145 --> 21:56.523
Right there.
And I've not been able to look at myself

21:57.482 --> 22:01.236
in a mirror in a suit
and ever say that, ever.

22:02.321 --> 22:04.364
Good. That makes me so happy.

22:04.448 --> 22:05.282
Okay.

22:06.199 --> 22:09.453
