25:02.876 --> 25:06.296
they were adamant
about needing to have a surgery letter.

25:06.838 --> 25:09.966
Then the woman said something to me
along the lines of,

25:10.050 --> 25:13.887
"I'm not gonna do this,
come back when you're complete."

25:14.387 --> 25:15.639
-What the hell?
-Yeah.

25:15.931 --> 25:21.478
It's heartbreaking because all he wants is
for the gender on his license

25:21.561 --> 25:24.397
to match the person he is
and the person we see.

25:24.481 --> 25:27.776
I'm gonna be walking out
with a male license today.

25:27.859 --> 25:28.860
Hundred percent.

25:29.361 --> 25:31.696
We're talking about a driver's license,

25:31.780 --> 25:34.741
but this is such
a life-changing moment for Skyler.

25:38.954 --> 25:42.749
The decision that is made
is gonna affect Skyler in ways

25:42.832 --> 25:45.919
that we take for granted every single day.

25:47.003 --> 25:49.172
-You said gender change?
-Yes, ma'am.

25:49.256 --> 25:51.758
So, I've got my social.

25:52.300 --> 25:57.305
A single card that is basically
your pass to get a job,

25:57.389 --> 26:00.475
go into a bar, get on a flight.

26:00.558 --> 26:02.894
[Skyler] So, I've got my birth certificate

26:02.978 --> 26:06.815
