and then my surgery letter.

26:16.825 --> 26:18.451
-It worked?
-Yeah. I got it.

26:18.535 --> 26:20.453
-Yes!
-Yeah, we're good, man.

26:20.537 --> 26:21.454
We're good.

26:21.538 --> 26:23.456
-Congratulations.
-Thank you.

26:23.540 --> 26:29.504
One little marker right there changes
a lot of experiences for me

26:29.587 --> 26:31.214
in my day-to-day life.

26:31.298 --> 26:36.553
The amount of times that you have
to show identification, or job hunting,

26:36.636 --> 26:41.224
like walking into a job interview
and knowing that if I get it,

26:41.308 --> 26:44.686
there's a chance they're gonna
take it away when I pull this ID out.

26:44.769 --> 26:47.188
Like, that's happened to me before.

26:47.772 --> 26:50.191
