27:47.916 --> 27:48.750
And then...

27:48.833 --> 27:50.418
-That's neat.
-Right?

27:50.543 --> 27:52.462
-Keep your pants organized.
-Cool.

27:52.545 --> 27:56.216
And the thing is this also allows you
to let go of things,

27:56.299 --> 27:59.052
'cause when you can't see everything
